title: Rust n' Wood
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, International, Asian, Filipino, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Slow food cafe near the entry of Lumiang Cave, a 20-minute walk from the town centre. Offers hot and cold drinks, salads and warm dishes. Upon request, Italian-Filipino fusion pasta, kimchi ramen, and japchae can be made vegan.
